        <h1>SHIMLA CITY SIGHTSEEING TOUR</h1><p>
       Verdant scenery, salubrious weather, snow-clad hills and an old-world charm, Shimla has always enticed nature lovers for 
       years. Thick covers of oak and pine that spread across the city are great for soaking in the peace and serenity. If short 
       hike is something that interests you, venture on a trek to the tranquil ‘Chadwick Falls’ that is located just 7 km from the 
       main city. Aesthetic beauty, serene vibes and musical chirps of birds here are sure to leave you with that much needed 
       solace.</p></div>   
